# Cursor — UI design only

Apply **only** when designing, styling, or building visual UI for this site.

**Do not apply** for config, content, analytics, scripts, or non-visual edits.

## Activation

- User asks to design UI, apply the design system, or change look and feel
- Editing: `_sass/**`, `_includes/**`, `_layouts/**`, `assets/css/**`, `index.html`, `design/**`

## Source of truth

Read `design/design-system.md` before UI changes. Style: **Organic / Natural** (wabi-sabi, earth palette, soft shadows, grain texture).

## Stack

Jekyll + SCSS + HTML includes. Map tokens to SCSS; match `_sass/_base.scss` and skins.

## File-scoped rule

Follow `.cursor/rules/design-ui.mdc` on UI paths (auto-attached via globs). Use @Codebase on `_sass/`, `_includes/`, `_layouts/` for component context.
